ed to that of  it has superior intergranular corrosion resistance and is used for industrial devices chemical equipments and lng tanks etc j  cr  ni  cuit has superior formability due to its added cu content and is used for the materials for deep drawing such as kitchen sinks and thermos bottles etc   cr  ni  moit has superior corrosion resistance and pitting resistance due to the added mo and increased ni contents and the excellent hightemperature strength so it is widely used for water pipelines equipment for manufacturing chemicals and coastal area facilities etc l  cr  ni  mo  lcl has superior intergranular corrosion resistance due to its low content of carbon compared to  steel and it is used under the environments that there are lots of corrosive elements such as salinity and poisonous gas etc ln  cr  ni  mo  nplateas a kind of steel with the strength that is enhanced by adding nitrogen into l steel it is used for chemical equipments and storage tanks etc   cr  ni  tias a kind of steel with the intergranular corrosion resistance enhanced by adding ti into  steel it is used for heat exchangers and boiler covers etc xmj  cr  ni  sicoldrolledas a kind of steel with hightemperature salinity corrosion resistance and superior oxidation resistance it is used for the components of cars ships machines heaters and incinerators etc s  cr  nias a kind of steel with superior hightemperature oxidation resistance and hightemperature strength by increasing the cr and ni contents it is used for applications requiring heatresistance such as ships machinery and heat exchangers etc ferrite   cr  cas a representative kind of ferrite stainless steel it has superior formability and oxidation resistance and is used for various purposes and applications such as kitchenware western tableware interior and exterior materials for construction etc l  cr  ti  lcnit has good weldability and formability due to the added ti content and is mainly used for cars ships machinery heat exchangers and heat resistant devices etc l  cr  lcnas a kind of steel with weldability toughness of welded connections and formability enhanced by lowering c content in  steel and is used for container structural materials and interior or exterior materials em  cr  si  ti  lcit has superior hightemperature strength and oxidation resistance as well as formability by adding elements of si ti mn and cu etc in addition to lowering c and n contents and is used for the components of cars ships machines and various kinds of heatresistant devices jl  cr  cu  nb  lcnit has superior corrosion resistance formability weldability and hightemperature characteristics due to the cu and nb contents added into  steel so it is used for washing machines kitchen utensils home appliances and heatresistant devices etc l  cr  mo  ti  lcnsince mo ti and nb are added into the steel it has superior corrosion resistance drawability and weldability and is used for auto exhaust parts and electric home appliance   cr  ti  lcndue to added ti content it has superior corrosion resistance workability and weldability and is widely used for auto exhaust parts and ornamental pipes   cr  mo  nb  lcnas a kind of steel added with high cr and mo contents it has superior intergranular corrosion resistance and scc resistance and is used for tanks and hot water heaters etc nf  cr  ti  cu  sinbas a kind of stainless steel containing high cr content it has superior corrosion resistance and formability and is used for various purposes and applications such as elevators western tableware construction interior and exterior materials etc m  cr  mo  ti nb  lcncold rolledas a kind of steel containing high cr and mo contents it has superior corrosion resistance and is mainly used for the construction exterior and roofing materials at costal areas martensite   cr  cit is a representive type of martensite stainless steel it has superior drawability and is hardend through heat treatment b  cr  niit is possible to secure an appropriate level of quenchinghardening by adjusting the contents of mn and ni compared to that of  steel and is used for automatic motorbikes and disk breaks etc n  cr  c  nas a unique kind of steel with corrosion resistance and strength are improved compared to that of j and is used for western tableware knife j  cr  cas a kind of steel having high quench hardening compared to that of j it is used for the parts of machinery requiring abrasion resistance duplex ld  cr  ni  mo  nas a kind of ni and mo saving duplex lean duplex steel it has superior anticorrosion intergranular corrosion resistance and is used for applications like water pipelines seawater and chemical equipments etc jl  cr  ni  mo  nit contains voluminous elements strengthening the corrosion resistance such as cr mo and n etc and has superior resistance against corrosion from salinity scc pitting corrosion crevice corrosion abrasion and erosion etc thus it is mainly used for applications like desalinating chemical and food processing equipments inquiry adobe reader download companybusiness ethicsproducts  technologyinvestor relationssustainabilitypr room legal information digital brochure request reports annual report  posco all rights reserved kor eng chn jpn companycorporate overviewcorporate overviewvision of poscohistory of poscobrandbrand storyciceogreetingsceos messagecorporate governancecorporate governancebodinformation on corporate governanceposco affiliatesposco affiliatessteelectradeictenergymaterial  chemistrysupportposco overseasglobalasiaamericaeuropeafrica business ethicscode of ethicsceo messageethics charterpractice guidelinesmajor activitiesoperation of the ethical management systemeducation on corporate ethicsunethical act prevention systemexternal activities and resultsethics counseling centerreporting center for unethical behaviorreward systemreportcheck result products  technologyproducts of posco hot rolled steelsteel platewire rodcold rolled steelgalvanized steelelectrical galvanized st