 february  posco signed a memorandum of understanding with afferro mining inc with a view to developing iron ore resources is cameroon in november  the completion of steel plant construction in cilegon indonesia is scheduled it is predicted that the annual production capability of this plant will be  million tons of molten iron on july   the movingin ceremony of  large steel structured pillars surrounding integrated steel mill furnace was held operationsedit head officeedit poscos headquarters along with the posco center form the brain of the company overseeing major tasks such as the management planning and finances of the steelworks at pohang and gwangyang the construction of posco headquarters at  goedongdong namgu pohang was completed on april   and has since become a structure that symbolizes the entire company posco centeredit winner of the  seoul architectural award for its progressive combination of modern design and ecofriendly engineering posco center is regarded as koreas first stateoftheart intelligent building this landmark in the heart of southern seouls teheran valley hightech venture corridor also hosts a wide variety of free cultural programs events and exhibitions throughout the year pohang and gwangyang steelworksedit gwangyang steelworks pohang  constructed in four phases between april  and february  along koreas southeast coast the nations first integrated steelworks has produced  million tons of pig iron through march   enough to build some  million compact cars crude steel production    million tons gwangyang  constructed in four phases between september  and october  on koreas southern coast the nations second integrated steelworks is among the worlds most advanced gwangyang focus on manufacturing automotive steel highstrength structure steel api line pipe steel and other strategic product categories crude steel production    million tons subsidiariesedit posco daewoo posco ec posco energy posco chemtech posco ict posco ps posco mtech posco c