ood poscothainox’s stainless steel products suitable for this application include austenitic grades  l l as well as ferritic grade  posre and nf food processing  medical equipment the smooth surface and chemical stability of stainless steel helps eliminate bacteria growth thus providing safety and hygiene required by the food and beverage as well as medical equipment industries for these application purposes poscothainox’s austenitic grades  l  as well as ferritic grades   l are perfect answers heavy industry energy  environment stainless steel with special properties is required for heavy chemical and energy industries gas oil nuclear etc it must offer safety and high heatresistance or provide mirrorfinished surface for the production of the environmentfriendly solar energy poscothainox’s stainless steel products suitable for this application include austenitic grades  l  and j architecture building  construction a large variety in terms of types grades thickness surface finishes and characteristics of stainless steel makes it ideal for architectural and construction applications as well as for use in interior and exterior design poscothainox’s austenitic grades   l as well as ferritic grades  nf and l not only make the creativity of architects and engineers come true but also fulfill endusers’ satisfaction terms of use  privacy policy copyright   poscothainox public company limited all rights reserved recommend web browser ie firefox chrome safari facebook twitter poscothainox site map  poscocom home       sustainability       investor relations       people  career       contact us marketing poscothainox brand marketing product distribution products  applications austenitic stainless steel ferritic stainless steel applications production  quality production process technical facilities total quality about us corporate profile vision milestones news  activities gallery products applications austenitic stainless steel ferritic stainless steel applications home  pro