 tons of galvanized steel sheet a year for automakerscitation needed the venture will be poscos first wholly owned steelplate plant in north america posco began construction in early  and started operations in  producing galvanized and galvannealed steel on june   posco completed the construction of its sixth continuous galvanizing line cgl at its gwangyang mill in the south jeolla province with this new addition posco becomes the no producer of sheetsteel just behind arcelormittal in early  warren buffetts berkshire hathaway purchased a  stake in posco in  they sold their share in february  posco signed a memorandum of understanding with afferro mining inc with a view to developing iron ore resources is cameroon in november  the completion of steel plant construction in cilegon indonesia is scheduled it is predicted that the annual production capability of this plant will be  million tons of molten iron on july   the movingin ceremony of  large steel structured pillars surrounding integrated steel mill furnace was held operationsedit head officeedit poscos headquarters along with the posco center form the brain of the company overseeing major tasks such as the management planning and finances of the steelworks at pohang and gwangyang the construction of posco headquarters at  goedongdong namgu pohang was completed on april   and has since become a structure that symbolizes the entire company posco centeredit winner of the  seoul architectural award for its progressive combination of modern design and ecofriendly engineering posco center is regarded as koreas first stateoftheart intelligent building this landmark in the heart of southern seouls teheran valley hightech venture corridor also hosts a wide variety of free cultural programs events and exhibitions throughout the year pohang and gwangyang steelworksedit gwangyang steelworks pohang  constructed in four phases between april  and february  along koreas southeast coast the nations first integrated steelworks has produced  million tons of pig iron through march   enough to build some  million compact cars crude steel production    million tons gwangyang  constructed in four phases between september  and october  on koreas southern coast the nations second integrated steelworks is among the worlds most advanced gwangyang focus on manufacturing automotive steel highstrength structure steel api line pipe steel and other strategic product categories crude steel production    million tons subsidiariesedit posco daewoo posco ec posco energy posco chemtech posco ict posco ps posco mtech posco cc snnc posmate posco terminal posco plantec pnr posco ast posco tmc posco ac entob posri posco capital posco ee posco humans posco engineering major competitorsedit arcelormittal nippon steel jfe group nucor corporation tata steel bhushan steel thyssenkrupp essar steel see alsoedit list of steel producers list of south korean companies economy of south korea history of the steel industry current referencesedit  a b c key statistics financeyahoocom retrieved    dead link  dead link  global  companies   fortune cnn   designing public procurement policy in developing countries how to foster  booksgooglecom  p  retrieved    a b matles savada andrea shaw william eds  south korea a country study diane publishing p  isbn x   대일청구권 자금 쓴 기업들 징용피해 지원은 ‘나몰라라’ companies benefitted by the japanese loan and grant disregard the victims of conscription the hankyoreh may     청구권자금백서 claim fund white paper economic planning board december     the role of yen loan for the rapid economic growth of korea pdf japan bank for international cooperation july  p    dead link  young university rankings   times higher education the times higher education retrieved    web page of campaign for survival and dignity on the legal implications of the project forestrightsactcom retrieved  april    gopalakrishnan shankar  warning bell posco more a curse than a blessing economictimesindiatimescom retrieved    iron and steal th